<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Pyramid Chart Demo
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>
Pyramid chart is similar to the funnel chart. It is often used for geographical purposes. The Pyramid Chart type displays the data which when totalled will be 100%. This type of chart is a single series chart representing the data as portions of 100%, and this chart does not use any axes.
</Paragraph>



